{"tid":676242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡路牌疑現簡體字？　網民嬲爆","createTime":"2018-05-24T08:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T17:28:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":364,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff7020a3e83b76e259b07f27a16a5c1987ce9c9","tid":676242,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/photo/bkn-20180524154500639-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180524155339\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180524%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180524154500639-0524_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180524155339&h=f648423e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明冇過境，但揸揸吓車見到有簡體字路牌，會唔會當堂嚇一跳？近日有網民發現，紅磡有警告路牌出現簡體字，質疑政府「咁都搞得錯」？ <br />\n<br />\n社交專頁「福佳與林忌創作」於星期四（24日）上載圖片，圖中可見於紅磡暢運道近置富都會，有警告路牌的「檢」字，被標示為簡體字「检」。<br />\n<br />\n相片一出，旋即引起網民熱議。有網民笑指，「睇唔明係咪唔會被檢控」、「個牌應該係假嘅」，又有人鬧爆政府「是是但但」，希望有關部門能盡快更正。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/bkn-20180524154500639-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180524%2Fbkn-20180524154500639-0524_00822_001.html&d=l%2Bs1Dl%2BLTlmF99EQBzEaT49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9f2791e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180524/bkn-20180524154500639-0524_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0f85db02a461a4647fa806bb4037409c9e564c7d","tid":676242,"uid":108347,"like":25,"dislike":128,"score":-103,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"港豬理得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 殘體字未殘體字，最緊要個市繼續向上，唉唔講，要番工"},{"pid":"aa44a0d811bd06ba40098e1b2e7e405bbdbf4e49","tid":676242,"uid":4357,"like":197,"dislike":2,"score":195,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"d字體好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg